'''Cadjan''' are [[woven mat (disambiguation)|woven mats]] made from [[coconut palm]] leaves, used for roofing and walls. Cadjan houses were available in many [[Asia]]n countries in past, but with [[Land development|development]] these houses are now limited to very [[rural area]]s in [[India]], [[Sri Lanka]] and a few other Asian countries.

